  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of a range of doses of
      SK-0403 in subjects with type 2 diabetes that are not adequately controlled on metformin
      alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
